{
  "stem": "20710.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was just everything was like a very unstable time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was-- there was nothing going on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was sort of like we were trapped and we just didn't do nothing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We just waited what the future's going to bring.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just around home and just talking to-- to friends, to neighbors, what-- what to expect.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody was in the same position.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody was very frightened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- but we were hoping, maybe some miracle is going to happen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To what?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, there was no place to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no, just a minute.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Let me-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] no, there was no place to go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then in 1941, the Germans, I think it was in June or July, so then they attacked the-- the-- the Russians.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they started the war with Russians.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then when we went through the same thing, the planes were, you know, it was-- it was like a-- a war in the air, you know.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that time, some people start to-- to-- to run, to go like with the Russians.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in fact, an uncle of my and my middle brother, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] because there are no cars and no things, just horse and buggies and all this, they packed a lot of things.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they said they're going to Russia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But usually the men, because they-- they always felt that the woman are more safe, you know, when-- when the Germans are going to come.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so the men run away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So this uncle, he lived in Lwow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he came that time to Hanaczow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he dealed a lot that time before the war with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
